  w("construct","/kənˈstrʌkt/","建造，构建","struct",[b("con-","prefix","共同"),b("struct","root","建造")],[e("They plan to construct a bridge.","他们计划建一座桥。"),e("Children learn to construct sentences.","孩子们学习造句。")]),
